    "However, the generation of such a concept using ChatGPT requires curiosity from human authors and the ability to formulate the right questions in order to get clear answers.",
    "It is important to ask chatbot consistently and follow the logic of the story.",
    "The chatbot effectively combines incompatible ideas and creates unobvious and extraordinary story concepts.",
